data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in the lovely Kingsridge West Phase II addition.  The living space opens to the dining and kitchen which is perfect for entertaining. The kitchen contains a large island, beautiful granite countertops and walk in pantry! Enjoy the large primary suite and the impressive, oversized shower. The secondary bedrooms are roomy as well with nice sized closets.  Carpet and faux wood tile throughout with the modern and natural gray and white color scheme.  At the end of the day, sit on the large covered patio and wind down. The backyard is spacious with plenty of room to add a storage building, store a boat or RV on the side. Home has security system through Vivent, Schedule your tour today!
